rush, we could take a walk.


13
00:04:24.274 --> 00:04:26.572
Play a little chess or something.

14
00:04:27.911 --> 00:04:30.243
Sure. Marg?

15
00:04:30.414 --> 00:04:33.076
-Can you take over the register?
-Sure, Howard.


16
00:04:33.250 --> 00:04:35.241
I mean, unless you're too busy.

17
00:04:35.419 --> 00:04:37.546
For you?
Are you kidding?


18
00:04:40.824 --> 00:04:43.349
-It's good to see you.
-You too.


19
00:04:43.527 --> 00:04:45.222
-Hey, Howard.
-Yeah?


20
00:04:45.396 --> 00:04:48.365
What's the price on
the Kid Gavilan-Basilio fight?


21
00:04:48.532 --> 00:04:52.093
-It's 8-to-5, Gavilan.
-I'll take Basilio five times.


22
00:04:52.269 --> 00:04:54.965
Okay, you got it.

23
00:04:57.674 --> 00:04:59.301
You never change.

24
00:05:03.881 --> 00:05:05.872
It's your move.

25
00:05:08.185 --> 00:05:09.743
Howard, I can't work anymore.

26
00:05:10.754 --> 00:05:13.279
Yeah?
What, like writer's block?


27
00:05:13.457 --> 00:05:14.981
No.

28
00:05:15.159 --> 00:05:18.754
-Well, what? You're not sick, are you?
-I'm blacklisted.


29
00:05:18.929 --> 00:05:23.025
-Yeah, all right, but you feel okay.
-I feel terrible.


30
00:05:24.201 --> 00:05:26.192
But you're healthy,
besides your ulcer.


31
00:05:26.370 --> 00:05:28.270
Howard, they won't buy my scripts.

32
00:05:28.439 --> 00:05:30.930
I'm on a blacklist.
You know what that means?


33
00:05:31.108 --> 00:05:35.477
It's a list of names. The studios have
them, the networks, the ad agencies.


34
00:05:35.646 --> 00:05:38.479
You're on the list, you're marked.
You don't work.


35
00:05:38.649 --> 00:05:41.140
So, what difference does
it make if I'm healthy?


36
00:05:41.485 --> 00:05:44.215
Well, you know,
it makes a difference.


37
00:05:44.588 --> 00:05:46.715
So, what are you blacklisted for?

38
00:05:48.659 --> 00:05:52.026
-I'm a communist sympathizer.
-Well, you always were.


39
00:05:53.063 --> 00:05:55.725
Well, it's not so popular anymore.

40
00:05:57.301 --> 00:06:01.169
Hey, how many times have I told you?
Take care of number one.


41
00:06:04.575 --> 00:06:06.202
So, all right, who can you sue?

42
00:06:07.211 --> 00:06:08.701
Nobody.

43
00:06:08.879 --> 00:06:10.972
Nobody admits there's a blacklist.

44
00:06:11.148 --> 00:06:14.083
I mean, they just say,
"Your script's not good enough."


45
00:06:14.251 --> 00:06:16.981
"You're not right for the assignment."

46
00:06:17.154 --> 00:06:19.349
Hey, I know some people.

47
00:06:19.523 --> 00:06:21.047
They're not exactly people...

48
00:06:21.225 --> 00:06:25.093
...but for $50 they'll break a few legs,
and you're not bothered anymore.


49
00:06:25.262 --> 00:06:27.389
-That's not what I need.
-You need money?


50
00:06:27.564 --> 00:06:30.328
I know a stock which is low now,
but it's going up.


51
00:06:30.501 --> 00:06:32.059
I need another name.

52
00:06:37.107 --> 00:06:39.439
Yeah, I can see that.

53
00:06:40.277 --> 00:06:41.972
Rappaport.

54
00:06:42.145 --> 00:06:44.807
-Arnold Rappaport.
-Pseudonyms don't work.


55
00:06:44.982 --> 00:06:48.440
They know we're all changing
our names. I need a real person.


56
00:06:53.357 --> 00:06:54.949
Of course.

57
00:06:55.125 --> 00:06:57.719
Someone they can believe
and I can trust.


58
00:06:57.895 --> 00:07:00.329
-Naturally.
-Now, listen...


59
00:07:00.497 --> 00:07:03.864
-...I wouldn't ask you--
-Who would you ask? I'd be insulted.


60
00:07:05.569 --> 00:07:08.265
-Nobody would know, just us.
-When do we start?


61
00:07:08.438 --> 00:07:11.771
Wait a minute. You'd better find out
what you're getting into.


62
00:07:11.942 --> 00:07:14.934
-You put my name on your scripts.
-It's not that simple.


63
00:07:15.112 --> 00:07:17.512
I write the scripts,
send them in your name...


64
00:07:17.681 --> 00:07:20.149
-...they buy the scripts, right?
-It's perfect.


65
00:07:20.317 --> 00:07:22.410
-They'll wanna meet the writer.
-So?


66
00:07:22.586 --> 00:07:24.781
You're gonna have to go
and be the writer.


67
00:07:24.955 --> 00:07:27.856
