152
00:11:42.078 --> 00:11:43.602
-Marvelous script.
-Thank you.


153
00:11:43.780 --> 00:11:45.748
-Hecky Brown.
-Who plays with himself.


154
00:11:45.916 --> 00:11:49.181
-Who plays the narrator.
-Howie! Howie Prince!


155
00:11:49.352 --> 00:11:51.013
