It's been so long.


158
00:11:56.493 --> 00:12:00.156
-You know each other?
-Never saw this man before in my life.


159
00:12:00.764 --> 00:12:03.198
Seriously, Mr. Prince,
a first-class script.


160
00:12:03.366 --> 00:12:05.095
Thank you.
Thank you very much.


161
00:12:05.268 --> 00:12:09.034
