181
00:13:06.096 --> 00:13:09.759
I don't disembowel a writer's script.
I believe in the written word.


182
00:13:09.933 --> 00:13:13.232
-Absolutely.
-I need it tomorrow morning.


183
00:13:13.403 --> 00:13:15.337
But you be happy with it.

184
00:13:24.915 --> 00:13:29.113
-I really liked your script a lot.
-Oh, yeah? Thank you very much.


185
00:13:29.286 --> 00:13:31.880
Most of the stuff I read....

186
00:13:32.689 --> 00:13:35.123
I mean yours had substance.

187
00:13:35.292 --> 00:13:36.850
